  "dialogos": [
    {
      "id": 0,
      "personagem": "Raiha",
      "texto_en": "Miku-san, 'haitaaai!'",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "personagem": "Raiha",
      "texto_en": "...Like this?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Pretty good, I think.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Miku, Raiha too.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Ah...\\nFutaro...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "personagem": "Raiha",
      "texto_en": "Big bro, 'haitaaai!'",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "'Haitai?'\\nIt's high tide?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "personagem": "Raiha",
      "texto_en": "Ahaha!\\nWay off! Right, Miku-san?!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "I learned some words of the Okinawan language,\\nfrom one of the attendants\\nin the Native Okinawan Village.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "personagem": "Raiha",
      "texto_en": "The language is called 'Uchinaaguchi.'",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Yeah, I've heard of it.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "'Haitai' is a greeting that means 'hello.'",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "personagem": "Raiha",
      "texto_en": "Men say 'haisai' and women say 'haitai!'",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Interesting, it changes depending on the gender.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "personagem": "Raiha",
      "texto_en": "Big bro, 'haitaaai!'",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "'Haisaaai.'",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Teehee...\\nBoth of you are cute.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "personagem": "Raiha",
      "texto_en": "Now, time for a quiz, big bro!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Ohh?\\nHow sudden.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "personagem": "Raiha",
      "texto_en": "What does the phrase\\n'akisamiyo' mean in Uchinaaguchi?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "No idea.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Wow...\\nYou give up too easily.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "personagem": "Raiha",
      "texto_en": "Think about it a little...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "It's not something you figure out just by thinking about it, you need to do some research.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Well, I guess.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Just tell me what it means.\\nIt's unsettling not to know.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "personagem": "Raiha",
      "texto_en": "'Akisamiyo' means something like\\n'oh my' or 'how surprising.'",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 27,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "...There's no way I would've gotten that.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "When you're surprised, you sometimes say 'akisamiyo'\\nwithout thinking about it. It's kind of strange.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Some sort of word to make a command?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "personagem": "Raiha",
      "texto_en": "Unfortunately, that's incorrect!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Ugh... Wrong, eh.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Why do you think that?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 33,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "I had a feeling that the last part, 'miyo',\\nmight be telling someone to do something.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 34,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Well, that could be a possible interpretation.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 35,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Just tell me what it means.\\nIt's unsettling not to know.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 36,
      "personagem": "Raiha",
      "texto_en": "'Akisamiyo' means something like\\n'oh my' or 'how surprising.'",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 37,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "...There's no way I would've gotten that.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 38,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "When you're surprised, you sometimes say 'akisamiyo'\\nwithout thinking about it. It's kind of strange.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 39,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "...I have a bad feeling about this.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 40,
      "personagem": "Raiha",
      "texto_en": "A bad feeling?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 41,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Raiha, are you trying to make me say embarrassing things\\nin front of Miku with words I don't know?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 42,
      "personagem": "Raiha",
      "texto_en": "Huh? Like what?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 43,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Like...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 44,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "I-I love you, or something like that.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 45,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Whaaa...!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 46,
      "personagem": "Raiha",
      "texto_en": "Oh, I see! I could have done that!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 47,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "WHAT THE?!\\nSo that means my answer is WRONG?!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 48,
      "personagem": "Raiha",
      "texto_en": "Totally unrelated.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 49,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(NNAH! I messed up!\\n Now it's even more awkward...)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 50,
      "personagem": "Raiha",
      "texto_en": "True... I should've gone for 'dejisukisa.'\\nNot 'akisamiyo.' Mmmm. What a shame.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 51,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Hey, even I can understand this one!\\nIt's obvious when you say it!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 52,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 53,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "'Deji...sukisa...'",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 54,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Just tell me what it means.\\nIt's unsettling not to know.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 55,
      "personagem": "Raiha",
      "texto_en": "'Akisamiyo' means something like\\n'oh my' or 'how surprising.'",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 56,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "...There's no way I would've gotten that.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 57,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "When you're surprised, you sometimes say 'akisamiyo'\\nwithout thinking about it. It's kind of strange.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 58,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "For sure.\\nIt's natural for someone\\nwho grew up in Okinawa, though.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 59,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Did you learn any others?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 60,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Yes, a few.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 61,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "The word I like is 'Nankurunaisa.'\\nIt means to be positive\\nand believe that everything will work out.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 62,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "I've heard of that one.\\nIt has a positive meaning, huh.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 63,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "The sound is kind of gentle too.\\nI might try saying it to myself\\nwhen I'm feeling down.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 64,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Yeah, isn't that nice?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 65,
      "personagem": "Raiha",
      "texto_en": "Big bro.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 66,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "What's wrong?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 67,
      "personagem": "Raiha",
      "texto_en": "You and Miku-san are looking really good right now.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 68,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Y-yeah, I guess.\\nThanks to you.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 69,
      "personagem": "Raiha",
      "texto_en": "Keep up the good relationship with Miku-san, okay?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 70,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Okay...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 71,
      "personagem": "Raiha",
      "texto_en": "Fine, then.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 72,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "?\\nWhat's wrong, you two?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 73,
      "personagem": "Raiha",
      "texto_en": "It's nothing!\\nNankurunaisa!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 74,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "O-okay.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    }
  ]
